fbc-a3af-daff898a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将于下周对其在 10 月 7 日袭击和之前的失败中的行为展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/idf-to-initiate-investigation-into-its-conduct-during-oct-7-attack-and-preceding-failures/0000018d-c322-dfbc-a3af-dbe760800000</link><description>内部审查将在各军、旅和军种进行，由高级军官监督 ■ 审查的主题包括部队的战斗准备、到达攻击现场、部署以及战斗方式</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 21:33:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/idf-to-initiate-investigation-into-its-conduct-during-oct-7-attack-and-preceding-failures/0000018d-c322-dfbc-a3af-dbe760800000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩南部至少遭受两次空袭；以色列国防军称其目标是真主党武器库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/at-least-two-airstrikes-hit-southern-lebanon-idf-says-it-targeted-weapons-depots/0000018d-c2f6-d0dd-adff-d6feccd90000</link><description>以色列首席陆军发言人表示，对西顿附近武器库的空袭是为了回应真主党向以色列发射一架无人机</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 21:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/at-least-two-airstrikes-hit-southern-lebanon-idf-says-it-targeted-weapons-depots/0000018d-c2f6-d0dd-adff-d6feccd90000</guid></item><item><title>遭到真主党轰炸并遭到以色列军队破坏：为什么黎巴嫩边境附近城镇的居民对以色列国防军感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/bombed-by-hezbollah-wrecked-by-idf-residents-of-towns-near-lebanon-border-are-furious/0000018d-c295-dfbc-a3af-dad5413c0000</link><description>当地议会负责人和没有撤离的居民抱怨士兵的行为，称他们在没有与任何人协调的情况下进入城镇，造成了相当大的破坏——甚至在住宅和宾馆也是如此。军方正在努力将损失降到最低</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 19:49:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/bombed-by-hezbollah-wrecked-by-idf-residents-of-towns-near-lebanon-border-are-furious/0000018d-c295-dfbc-a3af-dad5413c0000</guid></item><item><title>首先是人质，还是哈马斯？只有一个答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-19/ty-article/.highlight/israels-top-priority-must-be-the-hostages-not-their-kidnappers/0000018d-c267-dfbc-a3af-dae781ed0000</link><description>以色列人需要政府至少承认这里最重要的事情：首先将我们所爱的人带回家，然后我们可以做出我们想要的所有宏伟声明，将绑架者绳之以法</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 19:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-19/ty-article/.highlight/israels-top-priority-must-be-the-hostages-not-their-kidnappers/0000018d-c267-dfbc-a3af-dae781ed0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 136 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-136/0000018d-c286-d756-a7ed-d7979f3d0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，由于需要疏散平民，拉法地面行动的准备工作将需要数周时间。如果单方面承认巴勒斯坦国，则达成奥斯陆协议 ■ 西班牙表示，如果欧盟未能就问题达成共识，它将制裁暴力定居者 ■ 战争结束 136 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 18:18:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-136/0000018d-c286-d756-a7ed-d7979f3d0000</guid></item><item><title>印度工人在以色列排队上班，引发安全担忧和道德问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/safety-concerns-and-moral-questions-arise-as-indian-workers-queue-up-to-work-in-israel/0000018d-b1fe-dc8c-a3df-f3ff42220000</link><description>空前数量的印度人希望用自己家乡的失业来换取以色列相对较高的工资——以色列希望他们能取代数万名巴勒斯坦工人。据一些候选人称，众所周知，穆斯林不会被考虑</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 17:01:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/safety-concerns-and-moral-questions-arise-as-indian-workers-queue-up-to-work-in-israel/0000018d-b1fe-dc8c-a3df-f3ff42220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队播放在加沙发现的视频，显示 Bibas 一家于 10 月 7 日被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/idf-airs-footage-found-in-gaza-showing-bibas-family-taken-hostage-in-first-days-of-war/0000018d-c1fc-dfbc-a3af-dbfd29e40000</link><description>Shiri 和 Yarden Bibas 以及他们 4 岁的孩子 Ariel 和当时 9 个月大的 Kfir 在 Nir ​​Oz 基布兹被绑架。这段视频显示了希里和红发儿童在汗尤尼斯被绑架的情景，这是哈马斯去年 12 月发布亚登的视频后首次出现</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:10:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/idf-airs-footage-found-in-gaza-showing-bibas-family-taken-hostage-in-first-days-of-war/0000018d-c1fc-dfbc-a3af-dbfd29e40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列灾难旅游需求量很大，但加沙边境社区的居民说“不要来”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-our-home-and-this-time-were-not-extending-invitations/0000018d-c143-df10-a99f-d7f33e030000</link><description>通常每年的这个时候，以色列人都喜欢前往西内盖夫观赏海葵花。但今年，正如一位当地人所说，“这就像在重症监护室的邻居家里举办派对一样”</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 15:53:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-our-home-and-this-time-were-not-extending-invitations/0000018d-c143-df10-a99f-d7f33e030000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争对以色列经济造成重创，2023 年第四季度经济增速急剧下降 19.4%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/gaza-war-hits-israeli-economy-with-19-4-drop-in-q4-of-2023/0000018d-c199-dfd7-a9fd-f39d2e500000</link><description>由于大量调动储备金和数万人流离失所，以色列 5000 亿美元的经济去年增长了 2.0%，而 2022 年将增长 6.5%</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 14:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/gaza-war-hits-israeli-economy-with-19-4-drop-in-q4-of-2023/0000018d-c199-dfd7-a9fd-f39d2e500000</guid></item><item><title>加沙评论后，外交部长将巴西总统标记为以色列不受欢迎的人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-marks-brazilian-president-as-persona-non-grata-in-israel/0000018d-c136-df10-a99f-d7f751e70000</link><description>巴西总统卢拉将以色列在加沙的战争比作“希特勒决定屠杀犹太人”，这引发了巴西驻大屠杀纪念馆大使的谴责以及总统的严厉谴责</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-marks-brazilian-president-as-persona-non-grata-in-israel/0000018d-c136-df10-a99f-d7f751e70000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列男子因轮奸 16 岁女孩被判处 22 至 14 年监禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-men-given-22-14-years-in-prison-over-gang-rape-of-16-year-old-girl/0000018d-c13c-dfd7-a9fd-f3bc96bf0000</link><description>两名三十多岁的犯罪嫌疑人将在法庭判决后对受害人进行赔偿。涉案的另外八名男子将在晚些时候被判刑</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-men-given-22-14-years-in-prison-over-gang-rape-of-16-year-old-girl/0000018d-c13c-dfd7-a9fd-f3bc96bf0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院辩论以色列占领的合法性；内塔尼亚胡：听证会损害自卫权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/top-un-court-begins-hearings-into-israels-occupation-of-palestinian-territories/0000018d-c0c4-df10-a99f-d7f7f67e0000</link><description>国际法院开始就以色列占领约旦河西岸、加沙和东耶路撒冷问题举行为期六天的听证会，前所未有的 51 个国家将在听证会上发言</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:49:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/top-un-court-begins-hearings-into-israels-occupation-of-palestinian-territories/0000018d-c0c4-df10-a99f-d7f7f67e0000</guid></item><item><title>两项可能推翻内塔尼亚胡政府的法律草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-draft-laws-that-could-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018d-c019-dfd7-a9fd-f39d96c60000</link><description>两项极不受欢迎的军事征兵法涉及以色列境内深刻的政治、安全和社会紧张局势，很可能成为内塔尼亚胡政府的压垮基石 — — 并将影响加沙战争的继续</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:26:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/two-draft-laws-that-could-bring-down-netanyahus-government/0000018d-c019-dfd7-a9fd-f39d96c60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列伞兵在加沙地带南部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/israeli-paratrooper-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018d-c095-df10-a99f-d7f7afcb0000</link><description>参谋军士。西蒙·什洛莫夫（Simon Shlomov）于2021年从哈萨克斯坦移民到以色列，当时是以色列陆军伞兵旅的一名孤独士兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/israeli-paratrooper-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza-strip/0000018d-c095-df10-a99f-d7f7afcb0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的助手向同事、媒体人员和议员的妻子发放持枪许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-aides-hand-out-gun-permits-to-associates-media-personnel-and-lawmakers-wife/0000018d-c05f-dfd7-a9fd-f3dfea4b0000</link><description>在其平台上赞扬极右翼部长本-格维尔的媒体人士提交的许可证申请疑似在快速审批过程中获得批准，其中一些申请不符合标准</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-aides-hand-out-gun-permits-to-associates-media-personnel-and-lawmakers-wife/0000018d-c05f-dfd7-a9fd-f3dfea4b0000</guid></item><item><title>虽然以色列避免讨论加沙战争“第二天”，但巴勒斯坦人正在制定一项计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-avoids-discussing-the-day-after-the-palestinians-are-working-on-a-plan/0000018d-c05d-dc8c-a3df-f27de4800000</link><description>由于担心其政治前途，哈马斯可能被迫加入巴解组织并承认其在加沙地带的地位。华盛顿、相关阿拉伯国家和巴勒斯坦组织目前正竞相为加沙的未来制定切合实际的工作计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:45:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/while-israel-avoids-discussing-the-day-after-the-palestinians-are-working-on-a-plan/0000018d-c05d-dc8c-a3df-f27de4800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在美国压力下抵制国际社会承认巴勒斯坦国的呼吁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-fighting-intl-call-to-recognize-palestinian-state-under-u-s-pressure/0000018d-bdee-dc8c-a3df-ffff03880000</link><description>以色列总理内塔尼亚胡发起了反对单方面承认巴勒斯坦国的运动，称各方之间的直接谈判是建立巴勒斯坦国的唯一途径。虽然这是以色列全面采取的一项受欢迎的举措，但它可能无助于阻止国际认可</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 03:50:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-19/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-fighting-intl-call-to-recognize-palestinian-state-under-u-s-pressure/0000018d-bdee-dc8c-a3df-ffff03880000</guid></item></channel></rss>